                    </div>
                    <div class="blog_para">
                        <p>Fiber optic cables are one of the fastest growing transmission media for new cable
                            installations and upgrades, including spine, horizontal, and even desktop applications.
                            Fiber has several advantages over copper. To date, our best home internet option has been
                            the love-hate wired connection that most of us are familiar with. 
